This product includes software originally developed at
https://github.com/peledies/homebridge-ambient-weather-sensors

This is a soft fork distributed at
https://github.com/bcourbage/homebridge-ambient-weather-sensors
and on npm as @bcourbage/homebridge-ambient-weather-sensors,
maintained by Bruno Courbage <bruno@courbage.net>.

The fork adds Homebridge 2.x / HAP 2.x compatibility, multi-station
naming, an opt-in websocket data source, CO2 / PM2.5 / PM10 sensor
coverage, and several UX / correctness fixes, while upstream pull
requests #21 and #22 remain unmerged. Once upstream merges the
compatibility work, this fork can be deprecated.

